title: MarketWatch - What the Midterm Elections Could Mean for Your Money
description: MarketWatch's Washington bureau chief Robert Schroeder discusses with Beacon Policy Advisors' Ben Koltun and Bowling Green State University's Melissa Miller the outlook for the midterm elections and what the outcome could mean for the economy and Americans' finances.
